<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <head>
    <title>CSS Image Values (Gradients): Interactive, transform: skew 15deg and scale .5x with transition</title>
    <link rel="author" title="Opera Software" href="http://www.opera.com/"/>
    <link rel="help" href="{{test.specurl}}"/>
    <meta name="flags" content="dom"/>
    <script src="../../support/peg.js"/>
    <script src="../../support/css-gradients-via-canvas.js"/>
    <style>
      div {
        width: 200px;
        height: 100px;
        transition: transform 1s;
        -o-transition: -o-transform 1s;
        transform-origin: 0 0;
        -o-transform-origin: 0 0;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      div:hover {
        transform: scale(.5) skew(15deg);
        -o-transform: scale(.5) skew(15deg);
      }
      .test {
        background-image: linear-gradient(orange, blue);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <h4>There should be two identical patterns below and behave the same on hovering (change size and slant).</h4>
    <div class="test"/><div class="ref"/>
  </body>
</html>